Ownert Agent: From the moment you enter a massive circular deorative stamp driveway, you see the canary Island palm trees that adorn the amazing topiary landscaping you just know this home isn't your simple cookie cutter type but a beautiful custom built gorgeous residence. This four thousand one hundred fifty one square foot under roof, with two thousand nine hundred thirty one of air condionting space with five hundred ninety seven sq, ft. of oversize garage space, plus five hundred eighty seven sq.ft of screen in patio with tile on the diagonial with tongue and grove cedar wood ceiling. As you enter the double wooden front doors into a small foyer that displays a unique living room the shape of a stop sign to the double French doors leading out to the patio. This is just the beginning of many angles leading you around this special home. Just to describe some of the other rooms so your family will get a photo of true luxury that await you as you wander thru this maze of beauty. A separate large dining room with arch Windows in which you will enjoy many a meals. A short walk to the kitchen which by the way has many cabinets to store your goods with a separate pantry. There is a hanging pot rack over a Island. The kitchen has light gray cabinets with Corian counters
That lead you with an open concept to a livable and enjoyable family room with a wood burning fireplace with a rare black stone. There is a small bar counter and another small eating area adjacent to another set of double french doors that also lead out to the patio. The kichen also has a glass slider that open to a buffet area on the patio for entertainment purposes. The master bedroom is huge which can hold all of your bedroom furniture, and room for a sofa if you choose. This room also leads you to another set of French doors to your screen in patio. The four bedrooms are of   split style for your privacy. A indoor washer and dryer area with many extra cabinets that has a deep sink and closet. All floor area have tile on the diagonal or new wood floors in all rooms. This is a must see if you are looking for a gorgeous and loving home for you and your family to enjoy. A MUST SEE TODAY, IT WONT BE ON THE MARKET LONG DONT MISS OUT
